WEBVTT

00:05:29.792 --> 00:05:31.893
because whose grandmother calls them that?

00:05:31.917 --> 00:05:34.601
(Laughter)

00:05:34.625 --> 00:05:38.476
But I think that it was true.

00:05:38.500 --> 00:05:40.601
And it wasn't until years later,

00:05:40.625 --> 00:05:43.559
when I was in college
and studying basic physics,

00:05:43.583 --> 00:05:44.976
that I had a revelation

00:05:45.000 --> 00:05:46.268
that the world,

00:05:46.292 --> 00:05:48.143
at least the physical world,

00:05:48.167 --> 00:05:50.601
could be tested and understood,

00:05:50.625 --> 00:05:53.059
that I started to gain
a completely different sense

00:05:53.083 --> 00:05:54.393
of how the world worked

00:05:54.417 --> 00:05:56.393
and what my place was in it.

00:05:56.417 --> 00:05:59.601
And then later,
when I was able my own testing

00:05:59.625 --> 00:06:01.434
and understanding through research,